    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors achieved required gradation levels for MRL 2. Six factors were not assessed, which is acceptable per ASME V&V 40 Table 3 for Model Risk Level 2 with Medium model influence. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. Predicted RH values agree with experimental measurements within uncertainty bounds across all five operating points. The model is accepted for regulatory submission supporting worst-case hemolysis operating condition identification.",
